data.description: This 2 bed 1.5 bath ranch is just waiting for someone to complete some unfinished projects and make it their own. Sitting within a quiet, sought after neighborhood on a dead end cul-de-sac, this home would make a great investment, rental or forever home.  Wiring, plumbing, water heater  and bathrooms were all updated since 2017. The owner had to relocate prior to completing the installation of a basement drainage system.  The new sump pump and drainage system is in place and keeping the basement dry as it should, however, the debris from the project still are present in the basement and will need to be removed as well as the concrete still needs to be poured over the new system. There is definitely equity to gain in purchasing and completing the project. The basement is already plumbed for an additional bathroom.
